README -- GEOS-Chem Unit Tester: perl/ subdirectory 
27 Aug 2013
GEOS-Chem Support Team
geos-chem-support@as.harvard.edu


Perl Modules:
-------------

Dates.pm       : Module w/ various date & time routines
UtUtils.pm     : Module w/ common routines for the GEOS-Chem Unit Tester


Perl Modules:
-------------
gcUnitTest     : Main driver script for the GEOS-Chem Unit Tester
cleanFiles     : Script to clean old files from logs & jobs subdirectories
validate       : Script to difference GEOS-Chem output files


Input Files:
-------------
UnitTest.input : Input file for gcUntiTest.  You can create as many other
                 such input files as you need by copying & pasting.
                 
